---------------------------------------------------------------------------

by kalessil at 2015-12-25T22:14:10Z

^_^ have no better naming, but it's quote often happens that people re-inventing a wheel with PhpUnit:

assertTrue(false == ...) -> assertFalse(...)
assertTrue(false != ...) -> assertNotFalse(...)
assertTrue(... == ...) -> assertEquals(..., ...)
assertTrue(instanceof) -> assertInstanceOf
assertTrue(!empty) -> assertNotEmpty
assertFalse(file_exists) -> assertFileNotExists

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

by keradus at 2015-12-25T22:16:10Z

